# bmm-publisher

PHP CLI tool that reads openEHR BMM schemas and publishes class definitions as AsciiDoc, PlantUML, and YAML for the openEHR specifications website.

**Canonical reference: [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md)** — layout, architecture, standards, CLI commands, and workflows. Setup & commands: [README.md](../../README.md). AI working process: [docs/ai-workflow.md](../../docs/ai-workflow.md). Deep dev detail: [docs/development.md](../../docs/development.md).

**Critical:** `composer` / `php` / PHPUnit / PHPStan run **inside the dev container** only — use `make ci`, `make sh`, `make install`, or `docker compose -f .docker/docker-compose.yml run --rm app composer …`. Do not assume host PHP.
